ActMinistries and Ministers of State Act
SubjectOrder Assigning the Honourable Greg Rickford to Assist the Minister of Industry
PrecisOrder (1) terminating the assignment of the Honourable GREG RICKFORD, made by Order in Council P.C. 2013-864 of July 15, 2013; and (2) assigning the Honourable GREG RICKFORD, a Minister of State to be styled Minister for the Federal Economic Development Initiative for Northern Ontario, to assist the Minister of Industry, effective March 19, 2014.
